  <div class="content">
    <!-- <h1> This Week in Spring  - February 26th, 2013</h1> -->
<p> 
Welcome to another installment of <EM>This Week in Spring!  </EM>It's been an exciting  two weeks  for Hadoop content - Hadoop enthusiasts should check last week's post for an HD quality replay of <a href="http://www.springsource.org/node/3814"> Building Big Data Pipelines with Spring Hadoop</a> from SpringOne 2GX 2012.</p>
