	<LI> <EM>Krishna's Blog</EM> has a nice <A href="http://krishnasblog.com/2013/02/22/junit-testing-of-spring-mvc-application-introduction/">post on JUnit testing Spring MVC applications</a>.   
		
  </LI>
	


